{
  "texts": [
    "OASIS (Marcus et al. 2007) It is a library of neuroimaging and clinical data on dementia.",
    "It includes diagnostic data from neuroimaging scans, such as MRI and PET images, and also cognitive testing and clinical evaluations.",
    "OASIS is a valuable resource for researchers exploring the early detection, and diagnosis of dementia.",
    "It is also used in the development of new biomarkers and therapeutic targets.",
    "Omnibus (Chang et al. 2017) Gene expression omnibus (GEO) is a public database of gene expression information."
  ]
}